/* Table: CAD_DWG */
/*==============================================================*/
create table CAD_DWG
(
DWGID NUMBER(32) not null,
"DWGType" NUMBER(32),
"DWGName" NVARCHAR2(200),
"DWGDesc" NVARCHAR2(2000),
"MallID" NUMBER(32),
"BuildingID" NUMBER(32),
"FloorID" INTEGER,
"Version" VARCHAR2(200),
"MajorVersionNum" INTEGER,
"MinorVersionNum" INTEGER,
"RevisionVersionNum" INTEGER,
"StartTime" TIMESTAMP,
"EndTime" TIMESTAMP,
"DWGPath" NVARCHAR2(500),
"DWGGuidName" VARCHAR2(200),
"IsNewest" INTEGER,
"Enable" INTEGER,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32),
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
"Bounds" varchar2(4000),
constraint PK_CAD_DWG primary key (DWGID)
);

comment on column CAD_DWG."DWGType" is
'1：物业建筑结构CAD图
2：招商可视化CAD图';

comment on column CAD_DWG."DWGPath" is
'例如：1009（商场编码）/guid.dwg';

comment on column CAD_DWG."DWGGuidName" is
'guid.dwg';

comment on column CAD_DWG."IsNewest" is
'1：是
0：否';

comment on column CAD_DWG."Enable" is

0：停用';
